02:48.310 --> 02:49.250
Sudah lapar sekali.

02:49.280 --> 02:50.250
Cepat makan.

02:50.270 --> 02:50.970
Makanlah.

02:51.010 --> 02:51.570
Makanlah.

02:51.590 --> 02:52.310
Lu Yan,

02:52.510 --> 02:53.120
